      <title>Possible Bug?</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/noveniniupdate/forum/general/possible_bug</link>
      <description>Hi.&#13;
We use this extension for our projects and are very happy indeed. However we do have an issue related to the file image.ini.  It seems this file is not repected somehow , therefore the actual reference to image magick is not updated correctly on our production server when we run the update via comand line.&#13;
&#13;
The file image.ini in settings/* is updated (timestamp indicated this), but the value is not changed according to the xml source.&#13;
&#13;
Could you test and check if you are able to reproduce this bug?&#13;
&#13;
Thanks.&#13;
Lars</description>
