      <title>Changelog in version 2.0</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/noveniniupdate/forum/general/changelog_in_version_2_0</link>
      <description>Hi all&#13;
&#13;
Here is the changelog for the brand new version 2.0 of this extension :&#13;
&#13;
- Global refactoring, with interfaces, exceptions, etc...&#13;
- CLI script to do the update. It also can list environments and params.&#13;
- Ability to edit a single param has been removed because it duplicates the built-in &lt;i&gt;INI editing&lt;/i&gt; feature in the admin.&#13;
</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Jérôme Vieilledent)</author>
